test_large_range:
assert [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, ...] == [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 2
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  + [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  ?  ++++++
test_even_range:
assert [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, ...] == [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 4
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14]
  + [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
